Introduction

LIVE HIGH (Korean: 리브하이) is a four-member girl group formed by Red Creative Company (now known as Crayon Star Entertainment). They debuted on July 30, 2013 with the single "Hakuna Matata". LIVE HIGH has been inactive since June 2019.
